            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "The `example.lua` script above can be simplified. The `redrawstatus` call can be moved to the `CursorMoved` autocmd, and the `OptionSet` autocmd can be removed.\r\n\r\n```lua\r\nvim.api.nvim_create_autocmd('CursorMoved', {\r\n  callback = function()\r\n    vim.defer_fn(function()\r\n      for i = 0, 20 do\r\n        vim.o.textwidth = 80\r\n        vim.cmd('redrawstatus!')\r\n      end\r\n    end, 0)\r\n  end\r\n})\r\n\r\n-- <INSERT MANY BLANK LINES>\r\n```",
